8TH JULY 2010
=====================================
Version 1.0.0 stable release

Changes:
. General fixes to missing files on gem install due to error in Rakefile

. Added some example code in examples folder

. Added in extra return statements at the end of each Topic action as EM reactor loop returns nil
on ruby 1.8.7 Enterprise Edition on 64 bit machines

. Added set_attrs action in Topic to allow user to set attributes for each Topic

. Added in JSON support to parse the Policy attribute of a Topic